DataBase...
Data-Base is a software that stores data in organized manner so it become esasy to manage the data


there are two types of dataBase managment system 

RDBMS and non-RDBMS;

RDBMS = RDMBS(relational data base managment system) 
it is use to store data in the form of table

non-RDBMS = RDMBS(Non relational data base managment system)
 it is use to store data in the form of documents;


* MySQL is popular dataBase software use to handle data in relational manner(it stores data in form of table),
  and it is a RDMS(relational data base managment system)


